        "subject": "LU-12345 ec: Add EC library sanity test to test suite",
        "message": "LU-12345 ec: Add EC library sanity test to test suite\n\nAdd erasure coding library testing to the Lustre sanity test suite\nto validate Reed-Solomon functionality and enable automated testing\nof EC algorithms in CI/CD pipelines.\n\nThe test validates multiple RAID configurations and demonstrates\ncore EC operations including matrix generation, encoding, and\nrecovery algorithms.\n\nIncludes unified build system allowing the same EC source files\nto work in both kernel and userspace environments, eliminating\ncode duplication and maintenance overhead.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I910dde82ec2cad3ecb758c549ce97960bfa7d0b3\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
